				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Goblin king call and response. These lines are his calls, sort of a cross between a toast and a religious prayer. It means VICTORY! Rhaal'tuuch = rawl-TOOSH! Long oo like \"soon\", not like foot.Tuuch = toosh, same pronunciation."
